functions.name: ABS
functions.description:
ABS
Returns the absolute value of a number.

parameters.name: value
parameters.description: The number of which to return the absolute value.

functions.name: ACOS
functions.description:
ACOS
Returns the inverse cosine of a value, in radians.
Use the {@link DEGREES} function to convert the result of {@link DEGREES} into degrees.

parameters.name: value
parameters.description: The value for which to calculate the inverse cosine. Must be between -1 and 1, inclusive.

functions.name: ACOSH
functions.description:
ACOSH
Returns the inverse hyperbolic cosine of a number.

Related:
{@link TANH}

parameters.name: value
parameters.description: The value for which to calculate the inverse hyperbolic cosine. Must be greater than or equal to 1.

functions.name: AND
functions.description:
AND
Returns true if all of the provided arguments are logically true, and false if any of the provided arguments are logically false.

parameters.name: var_args_expressions
parameters.description: An expression or reference that represents some logical value, i.e. TRUE or FALSE, or an expression that can be converted to a logical value.

functions.name: AVERAGE
functions.description:
AVERAGE
Returns the numerical average value in a dataset, ignoring text.

parameters.name: var_args_values
parameters.description: values to use when calculating the average value.

functions.name: CEILING
functions.description:
CEILING
Rounds a number up to the nearest integer multiple of specified significance.

parameters.name: value
parameters.description: The value to round up to the nearest integer multiple of factor.

parameters.name: factor
parameters.description: The number to whose multiples value will be rounded.

functions.name: CHAR
functions.description:
CHAR
Convert a number into a character according to the current Unicode table.

parameters.name: number
parameters.description: The number of the character to look up from the current Unicode table in decimal format.

functions.name: CLEAN
functions.description:
CLEAN
Returns the text with the non-printable ASCII characters removed.

parameters.name: text
parameters.description: The text whose non-printable characters are to be removed.

functions.name: CODE
functions.description:
CODE
Returns the numeric Unicode map value of the first character in the string provided.

parameters.name: text
parameters.description: The string whose first character's Unicode map value will be returned.

functions.name: VERSIONINFO
functions.description:
VERSIONINFO
Returns version information about the app.
examples:
// returns Apple iPhone6,2 iOS 8.1 Fulcrum 2.7.0 2162
VERSIONINFO()
